{"name": "Burnable Squares by @apeblond 1", "description": "Burn your Burnable Square and get in exchange a Burned Square with a color that will depend on the gas price of Ethereum Mainnet at the moment of the transaction.

Anything over 15 gwei will make your square non-white.

Anything over 100 gwei will make your square black.

Anything in between... you got it.
